messages.messageBody:
Hello all!

Kathryn wanted to remind everyone that the Early Bird registration closes in just a couple of days. Save money and register! The early bird prices will remain in effect until Sunday night and will be changed on Monday.

Also, if you need a scholarship, apply soon. It gets harder to offer them the closer we get to the conference.
Our presenters this year include Peter Gray, Ren Allen, and the Kreams! And we'll be entertained by Carsie Blanton, a grown unschool and wonderful singer-songwriter!
